                </div>
                <div class="Item-BodyWrap">
                    <div class="Item-Body">
                        <div class="Message userContent">
                            <p>Oh, the leader had done it based on a vote, a vote he opened on some website, kept open for 15 minutes when nobody was online except him, and decided that it was a "unanimous" decision. It wasn't a racial thing, although he did want everyone to ACTUALLY learn Spanish, which, is an extreme thing to do for any arma unit I think you'll agree. It was more about the fact that I'd joined a unit that was based around SMU's/other special forces and small unit tactics, and the entire format just suddenly changed, as did most of the membership. In a nutshell, it just got ridiculous to me and quite a few of the original members and we all went our separate ways.</p>

<p>BTW the name of my own unit was actually US Army 1st CAG, just thought I'd make it more clear.</p>
